title: Lemony Snickets a Series of Unfortunate Events  - 2004 Xvid (inc
description: Based on the bestselling book series by Daniel Handler, the &quot;Snicket&quot; saga revolves around a pint-sized trio of orphans named Sunny, Klaus and Violet who find themselves fobbed off on a series of odd people, including Lemony Snicket, who narrates each of what has grown to a series of eight books since Handler debuted the first title in 1999. The recurring bad guy is a distant family relative named Count Olaf, who initially takes in the kids but clearly is trying to separate them from a family inheritance.
